description: Vuebnb is a clone of Airbnb built with Vue.js and Laravel. In this post, I'll give a high-level overview of how it works so you get a sense of what's involved in building a full-stack Vue/Laravel app.
name: Vuebnb: A Full-Stack Vue.js and Laravel App
